Richards Bay July Coal Exports Fell 27% From Year Ago

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-05T08:14:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/richards-bay-of-south-africa-s-july-coal-exports-fell-27-from-year-ago.html
Shipments from  Richards Bay  Coal
Terminal, on  South Africa ’s east coast, fell 27 percent in July
from a year earlier, according to Bloomberg calculations based
on  data published  on the terminal’s website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
